This folder contains all code (R scripts) accompanying the paper "Impacts of sea level rise on the world's shorebirds". 
Individual scripts are described in further detail below.

ANALYSIS.R
This R script contains the necessary code to calculate the basic statistics included in the paper (e.g., mean study length; 
number of studies for each stage of the annual cycle, species, flyway, etc.).

FIGURES.R
This R script contains the necessary code to produce Figures 2, 6, and S1. Please note that additional processing was performed 
in PowerPoint to produce the final version of Fig. 6 (i.e., to add the labels on the top and right side of the figure).
